# 👟 SoleSphere: Shoe Brand Review & Collection Management System

## Objective

This project manages shoe brands, personal reviews, and a wishlist of favorite sneaker models.

## Technologies Used

* MySQL
* SQL
* XAMPP
* Git
* GitHub

## Tables

* brands
* my_reviews
* wishlist

## Features

* Store favorite shoe brands.
* Add personal ratings and opinions.
* Maintain a wishlist.
* Perform JOIN and aggregate queries.

## Screenshots

See the `screenshots` folder for outputs and database views.
